### Registrar usuário CLIENTE
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sara@servicehub.com",
  "senha": "123456",
  "role": "CLIENTE",
  "nome": "Sara Gisele",
  "telefone": "(91) 99999-0000",
  "bairro": "Nazaré"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sara@servicehub.com",
  "senha": "123456"
}

### Criar cliente
POST http://localhost:8080/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Marcos Silva",
  "email": "marcos@servicehub.com",
  "telefone": "(91) 98888-1111",
  "bairro": "Umarizal"
}

### Listar clientes com paginação
GET http://localhost:8080/clientes?page=0&size=10&sort=nome,asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar diarista
POST http://localhost:8080/diaristas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Renata Costa",
  "email": "renata@servicehub.com",
  "telefone": "(91) 97777-2222",
  "bairro": "Batista Campos",
  "experiencia": "4 anos"
}

### Criar agendamento
POST http://localhost:8080/agendamentos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clienteId": 1,
  "diaristaId": 1,
  "dataServico": "2026-03-05",
  "status": "CONFIRMADO",
  "observacoes": "Apartamento 2 quartos"
}

### Criar avaliação
POST http://localhost:8080/avaliacoes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clienteId": 1,
  "diaristaId": 1,
  "agendamentoId": 1,
  "nota": 5,
  "comentario": "Excelente atendimento"
}
